    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>为了解救被封印的月之女神，与少女娜菲一起揭开神秘迷宫的谜团吧！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075000/extras/97b05e0e21cd5530c8a2181ae6aa3c67.poster.avif?t=1751099792\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075000/extras/97b05e0e21cd5530c8a2181ae6aa3c67.webm?t=1751099792\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075000/extras/97b05e0e21cd5530c8a2181ae6aa3c67.mp4?t=1751099792\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>■■■■游戏概要■■■■</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《娜菲 ～月光迷宫～》是一款VR动作解谜游戏，讲述玩家与见习巫女娜菲一起，为了解救被封印的月之女神而踏入充满机关与魔女刺客的神秘迷宫的冒险故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>■■■■你是传说中的勇者诺瓦里斯■■■■</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >虽然你被娜菲召唤到了这个世界，但因为她还只是见习巫女，召唤尚不完全。请运用她获得的「月之力」，帮助娜菲展开冒险。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>■■■■诺瓦里斯的能力■■■■</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>右手：月光护臂</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用「月之力」启动巨大机关，或解除封印装置。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075000/extras/07d5593e2f366d70bece9c0520f663a4.poster.avif?t=1751099792\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075000/extras/07d5593e2f366d70bece9c0520f663a4.webm?t=1751099792\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075000/extras/07d5593e2f366d70bece9c0520f663a4.mp4?t=1751099792\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>左手：吊坠</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >显示月光宝石获得量、月之等级与娜菲的状态。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075000/extras/31c60116ee082a81173a1750bb879e8f.poster.avif?t=1751099792\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075000/extras/31c60116ee082a81173a1750bb879e8f.webm?t=1751099792\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075000/extras/31c60116ee082a81173a1750bb879e8f.mp4?t=1751099792\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>■■■■与见习巫女娜菲的羁绊■■■■</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与娜菲「直接互动」才能获得的特殊效果。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当她在难以接触的地方时，可召回到身边继续前进。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▼变身为黑猫</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075000/extras/ccfdc20d281eb62a034771b1e000402f.poster.avif?t=1751099792\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075000/extras/ccfdc20d281eb62a034771b1e000402f.webm?t=1751099792\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075000/extras/ccfdc20d281eb62a034771b1e000402f.mp4?t=1751099792\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>▼伤害回复</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075000/extras/bb29afddad1a46438f78f5696328ee2a.poster.avif?t=1751099792\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075000/extras/bb29afddad1a46438f78f5696328ee2a.webm?t=1751099792\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075000/extras/bb29afddad1a46438f78f5696328ee2a.mp4?t=1751099792\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>▼交流互动</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075000/extras/97b05e0e21cd5530c8a2181ae6aa3c67.poster.avif?t=1751099792\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075000/extras/97b05e0e21cd5530c8a2181ae6aa3c67.webm?t=1751099792\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075000/extras/97b05e0e21cd5530c8a2181ae6aa3c67.mp4?t=1751099792\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>本作无激烈的画面变化，适合所有玩家轻松享受！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >快与娜菲一同展开冒险，拯救这个世界吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >也许娜菲正蜷缩着身子，像只猫咪一样在等你来……</p>",
